================================================================================
Operating System Compatibility:
================================================================================

This application is designed to work on:
- Windows 11 and above
- Ubuntu 24.04 and above

Platform-Specific Components:
- Windows: Uses SAPI5 speech engine (built into Windows)
- Linux: Uses eSpeak or eSpeak-NG speech engine (may require separate installation)

